 Also in many cases the Relation Tool is not the best or the only way to
 collect information about geometric facts.
 Nevertheless, GeoGebra already has support for such investigations, so
 it can be fruitful to demonstrate some of the statements with the Relation
 Tool as well.
\end_layout

